Package: anymeal
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cookbook database for storing recipes
 AnyMeal is a free recipe database software developed using
 SQLite3 and Qt5. It can manage a cookbook with more than
 250,000 recipes, thereby allowing to import, export, search,
 display, and print them. AnyMeal is available for GNU/Linux
 and Microsoft Windows.
